high_descs: Move to the white counter behind you.
Pick up the spatula from the counter top.
Move the refrigerator on the left
Open the refrigerator and place the spatula in the pan
Pick up the pan with the spatula and close the refrigerator door
Move to the counter top to the right of the sink
Place the pan on the counter top to the right of the sink
anns.task_desc: Put a spatula in a pan to the right of the sink.

high_descs: Turn right, move towards the sink on the other side of the room, then turn right and move to the center of the table to the right of the refrigerator.
Pick up the spatula located between the plate and the cup from the center of the table.
Turn left and move towards the dishwasher next to the sink, then turn right and face the refrigerator next to the table.
Open the refrigerator and place the spatula in the pan underneath the loaf of bread.
Pick up the pan containing the spatula from the refrigerator and close the refrigerator door.
Turn left and move to the dishwasher to the right of the sink.
Place the pan containing the spatula to the right of the sink between the spray bottle and the fork on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Place a pan containing a spatula on the counter.

high_descs: turn right, move forward a tiny bit, then turn right to face the white table
pick up the spatula from the table
turn left and head to the black refrigerator, then turn right to face the refrigerator
open the refrigerator and place the spatula on the pan
pick up the pan and spatula from the refrigerator and close the refrigerator
turn left and move forward to the countertop
put the pan and spatula on the countertop to the right of the sink
anns.task_desc: Place the pan/spatula on the countertop
